race.description: Kyneton Horse Of The Year Caboteur Mdn Plate
race.comment: HULKSTER (8) settled last at Geelong before making up a stack of ground beaten less than 2L over 1440m. Didn't have much luck at the business end and finally draws an inside barrier. In a top stable and is sure to keep improving. THINKING SENSATION (4) races forward and improved at Echuca narrowly beaten over 1300m. This is a bit harder but he is heading in the right direction and has claims. CORAL IMPACT (2) resumes and won a recent Flemington jumpout. Will be at his best over further but has good ability and may be more forward this time around. Keep safe. LANGLO CROSSING (9) looked a run short at Murtoa and he'll be tougher to beat today. Nolen is a key jockey switch.
